"    Synergistic interactions between an increase in cytosolic calcium (Ca[i]2+) and a decrease in adensine triphosphate (ATP) availability increase diastolic tension and can cause or exacerbate diastolic dysfunction.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
